<h1>About Melodic PHP</h1>
<p>Melodic PHP is a modern PHP 8.2+ framework built with the following principles:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Controller → Service → Query/Command</strong> layered architecture</li>
    <li><strong>CQRS</strong> data access pattern mirroring NHA.Backend</li>
    <li><strong>Dependency injection</strong> with constructor auto-wiring</li>
    <li><strong>JWT-based security</strong> with claims-based authorization</li>
    <li><strong>No facades, no mediator</strong> — direct, explicit code flow</li>
</ul>
